b) issue opening or closing;
c) advertisements;
d) underwriting;
e) sub-regulation (2) of regulation 5;
f) pricing;
g) dispatch of issue material; and
h) other such provisions related to offer of specified securities to the public. (4) The issuer shall obtain an in-principle approval from the stock exchanges on which it
proposes to get its specified securities listed.
